calc_stat.pl -- calculate statistics (i.e., how many bases are affected)
check_chain.pl -- The program checks chain files to have consistent chromosome lengths.
check_chrom_chain.pl -- The program checks chromosome lengths in chain file and .fa files.
check_map_file.pl -- The program checks map files for obvious inconsistencies.
check_chromosomes.pl -- Check created chromosomes and .map files
check_SNPs.pl -- checks whether SNPs are in place

